{"tid":2413880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"25歲女稱有怪風吹入下體 15分鐘後腹部隆起突然生得","createTime":"2021-02-19T04:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T06:05:21.000Z","uid":50386,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f98e5b5bac8d15488b80e6a0a5ac5e6b15074350","tid":2413880,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"印尼出現離奇無性懷孕事件，25歲印尼女子Siti Zainah表示有陣怪風吹入下體，肚子逐漸隆起引起劇痛，1小時後誕下女嬰始知自己懷孕。<br />\n<br />\nSiti Zainah稱有日完成下午的禱告後，便躺在地上休息，然後感受到一股怪風吹入下體，15分鐘後她的肚子隆起並強烈劇痛，她馬上到附近的診所求醫竟然誕下女嬰，重2.9公斤、健康狀況一切正常。 <br />\n<br />\n此宗無性懷孕事件震驚當地市民，警方質疑事件的真確性正進行調查，指Siti Zainah四個月前才跟前夫離婚，他們育有一子，有機會是與前夫所生。 Siti Zainah則表示自己完全無懷孕的徵兆，甚至經期仍然正常，認為是真主阿拉賜予的小生命。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/34844/25歲印尼女稱有怪風吹入下體-15分鐘後腹部隆起突然生得/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F34844%2F25%E6%AD%B2%E5%8D%B0%E5%B0%BC%E5%A5%B3%E7%A8%B1%E6%9C%89%E6%80%AA%E9%A2%A8%E5%90%B9%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%8B%E9%AB%94-15%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%BE%8C%E8%85%B9%E9%83%A8%E9%9A%86%E8%B5%B7%E7%AA%81%E7%84%B6%E7%94%9F%E5%BE%97%2F&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69HHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=476bb9d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://travel.ulifestyle.com.hk/news/detail/34844/25歲印尼女稱有怪風吹入下體-15分鐘後腹部隆起突然生得/</a><br />\n<br />\n聖母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9660416e2ed87a08aa8e2b2993ee0868580db5e5","tid":2413880,"uid":123848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:40:16.000Z","msg":"點解要差佬查<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0067474302bbceb2bafc3ebb1fbc6cb003a79ef8","tid":2413880,"uid":254371,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:40:49.000Z","msg":"你以為現代人咁易呃咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n古代人都係瑪利亞可以呃都下人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c